Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.71,0:23:22.67,zh,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1440,1026)}似的
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.09,0:23:29.52,zh,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.52,0:23:31.02,zh,,0,0,0,,你们笑什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.02,0:23:32.31,zh,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.31,0:23:35.83,zh,,0,0,0,,真是的 你们也太般配了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:35.83,0:23:36.82,zh,,0,0,0,,羡慕吧
